post_summaries.description: The image shows a close-up of a "Raw Vegan Irish Moss Corn Dawg" on a brown decorative plate. The corn dog is topped with zig-zagged lines of yellow mustard and red ketchup. The plate sits on a wooden surface, likely outdoors, with blurred bottles of sauce in the background.

The image shows a close-up of a raw vegan taco, featuring a colorful array of toppings like tomatoes, red onions, avocado, and a white sauce. The user, enzyme.333, captioned the post "Love these raw vegan tacos."

The image shows a plate of what appears to be a raw vegan sandwich. The plate has writing in what appears to be Amharic. The caption mentions it's a raw vegan white bread recipe that can be made quickly, and promotes ebooks.

The image shows a multi-tiered "cake" made entirely of fresh fruit, including watermelon, strawberries, grapes, blueberries, and dragon fruit. The post caption says it was a fun cake to make and that they highly recommend it.

The image shows enzyme.333 standing next to a woman (presumably @ying.yyz) on a balcony with a city skyline in the background. Enzyme.333 is holding a watermelon cake decorated with fruit. The caption mentions it was @ying.yyz's birthday and that enzyme.333 usually makes sprouted almond cake.
The image shows a person, presumably enzyme.333, launching a kickflip on a snowboard at Strawberry Park. There are skis visible in the background, suggesting a ski resort environment.
